Kenneth MacDonald (English actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kenneth_MacDonald_(English_actor) 0 Kenneth MacDonald (20 November 1950 – 6 August 2001) was an English-born actor who was best known for the parts of Gunner Nobby Clark in It Ain't Half Hot Mum and Mike Fisher in Only Fools and Horses.
